<title>mkcat.py</title>
<summary>Tarn Burton's mkcat.py</summary>
</head>

<para>Just a little <ulink url="mkcat.py">python script</ulink> to create an XML catalog
with URI lookups for a collection of files. Might
make user customization of DocBook XSL easier.</para>

<para>Example from docbook-xsl root:</para>

<programlisting>
$ python mkcat.py --base-uri=docbook-xsl-1.44 html/*.xsl
</programlisting>

<para>Creates a catalog file:</para>

<programlisting><![CDATA[<catalog ...>

<uri name="docbook-xsl-1.44/html/docbook.xsl"
uri="html/docbook.xsl"/>

.
.
.

</catalog>]]></programlisting>

<para>Might be useful....</para>

